title: Which Playoff Contenders Are Real and Fake? Plus, Play-In Tournament Preview. | Real Ones
description:
On the eve of the NBA Play-In Tournament, Logan and Raja discuss whether each of the top-ranked and highly regarded teams are real or fake Finals contenders (8:00). Then they do a preview of the play-in matchups (47:00).
Hosts: Logan Murdock and Raja Bell
Producers: Sasha Ashall and Mike Wargon
